        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          I’m Giovanni Amodeo — a capital markets strategist, C-suite operator, and trusted host to the world’s most influential investors.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          At ION Analytics, I convene conversations with senior LPs, GPs, founders, and corporate leaders — over 300 fireside chats annually for those who move markets.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Previously, as Chief Data Officer at ION Analytics, I unified data strategy across M&A, ECM, DCM, Infrastructure, and Compliance — integrating 30+ databases and leading a global team of 600 analysts and engineers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Earlier in my career, I was Global Editor-in-Chief at Mergermarket, where I scaled one of the industry’s largest editorial teams and launched the firm’s Editorial Analytics unit — combining proprietary content with strategic data insights.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Today, I operate where relevance meets relationship — building a curated global network of over 1,000 senior decision-makers, and enabling the kind of access, insight, and alignment that never makes it to stage.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Looking for signal over noise in global markets? Let’s connect.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
